JVM Memory:
------------
     - Method Area
         Stores class level info like className, parent class, method, variable static data information.
     - Heap Area
          All Objects are stored in this area.
     - Stack Area
         - For each thread a runtime stack is created.
         - Stack contains stack frames.
              - Method parameters
              - Local Variables
              - Return address(After the execution of method where the control should go.)   
