     - PC Register:
        Holds the address of currently executing instruction.
     -> Native method stack
            Native methods - these are the methods that are used to communicate with programs that are written other languages(like C, C++) Java communicating with OS.
          In order to store these native methods jvm uses native method atacks.   

Execution Engine:
-----------------
    It executes the .class files.
    Read byte code line by line uses data present in variuos memory areas it executes the instruction.
       1. Interpreter
            - Reads instruction line by line
            - Converts this into machine code.
            - Exutes the generated machine code instruction immediatley.
       2. JIT Compiler(Just in time compiler.)
